-- French Industry Minister to Meet PSA Labor Unions: JDD Reports
-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 2012-06-17T09:27:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-17/french-industry-minister-to-meet-psa-labor-unions-jdd-reports.html
French Industry Minister  Arnaud Montebourg  will meet with car-maker PSA Peugeot Citroen’s Aulnay
factory labor unions tomorrow to discuss the site’s fate,
Journal du Dimanche reported, citing the minister’s office.  The minister will meet with unions ahead of the June 28
works council meeting and the factory with 3,300 employees may
suspend activity, JDD said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helene Fouquet in Paris at 
 hfouquet1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vidya Root at 
 vroot@bloomberg.net  